name: Tally Bodnarec
tagline: A Geospatial Appications Developer Assignment for the British Geological Survey
body:
### Hey there...
Welcome to my assignment! I chose to host it on Gibhub Paages as I wanted to use this opportunity to build on the sills I have developed in a classroom based environment to produce something amazing to support my CV for the position of Geospatial Applications Developer at the BGS!

Have a look around,  hope you enjoy!

Tally
